import React, { Component } from 'react'; class ExploreTwo extends Component { state = { data: { preHeading: "Explore Local Collection", heading: "Discover Unique NFTs", btnText: "View All", btn_2: "Load More", exploreData: [ { id: "1", img: "https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmSrkuhtoQqwKUBkixXP6rVhBUxPnUPDuLgQHMvQJV5b4T", title: "Wrong Decision", owner: "QueenP", price: "1.5 ETH", count: "1 of 1", btnText: "Place a Bid" }, { id: "2", img: "https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmTSjRKJQ64Rjz5jFR1ShatSVqGtYcBNzkWqUaJSnUzUMJ", title: "FATE", owner: "ALLE", price: "2.7 ETH", count: "1 of 1", btnText: "Place a Bid" }, { id: "3", img: "https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmbFGxv25a688WHeCDCdCct8qx3srjycyvTdWXhzjisgDu", title: "Twisted", owner: "ASPblots", price: "2.3 ETH", count: "1 of 1", btnText: "Place a Bid" }, { id: "4", img: "https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmYP2jkvDBBEQ7KmeAK7DJwSnoK6z5fqopEdbv3ZGp4RAK", title: "Twenty", owner: "ObxArham", price: "1.8 ETH", count: "1 of 1", btnText: "Place a Bid" }, { id: "5", img: "https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmYwPwGo1J1MwGTFqy2y5RBoGucJtHyHywQCBhW3mERoJL", title: "Slowly", owner: "ChiefCommander", price: "1.7 ETH", count: "1 of 1", btnText: "Place a Bid" }, { id: "6", img: "https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmU15xJqCUu2aV155E7JV4Am7DkPb2ybExobbAf13CVCwX", title: "WITCHES", owner: "42", price: "3.5 ETH", count: "1 of 1", btnText: "Place a Bid" }, { id: "7", img: "https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmaDtWv9XToerpE6Y8av79cVJbZzhfHvXJSKmL8Vqa7FxQ", title: "Nero", owner: "ObxArham", price: "2.1 ETH", count: "1 of 1", btnText: "Place a Bid" }, { id: "8", img: "https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmXm3MRMuJQjJfBgn3TPSrWqVZYmWHzyaLeTToNE5N9SeR", title: "Eight", owner: "ObxArham", price: "2.9 ETH", count: "1 of 1", btnText: "Place a Bid" }, { id: "9", img: "https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmbDXbcoM4X8Xbdwf11nnnJQTVyqTxE2Ty9Ys47Ke9R7ZS", title: "Kingdom", owner: "42", price: "3.3 ETH", count: "1 of 1", btnText: "Place a Bid" } ] } }; render() { return (
{/* Intro */}
{this.state.data.preHeading}

{this.state.data.heading}

{this.state.data.btnText}
{this.state.data.exploreData.map((item, idx) => { return (
{/* Card Caption */}

{item.title}
Owned By
{item.owner}
{item.price} {item.count}
{item.btnText}
); })}
{this.state.data.btn_2}
); } } export default ExploreTwo;
